, pp. 3. Retrieved on 2009-02-08.</ref>和[[巴西|巴西]]東北部<ref name="Brazil">James Brian Elsner (1988). [http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1988PhDT........55E Analysis of Wet Season Rainfall Over the Nordeste of Brazil, South America.] University Of Wisconsin-Milwaukee. Retrieved on 2009-02-06.</ref>等等。
 
